{"data":{"id":"ChIJdxXRGNH2BFMRm6-OFl60Thk","types":["dentist","dental_clinic","medical_clinic","point_of_interest","doctor","health","establishment"],"nationalPhoneNumber":"(306) 700-3394","internationalPhoneNumber":"+1 306-700-3394","formattedAddress":"201 1 Ave S #401, Saskatoon, SK S7K 1K3, Canada","rating":4.9,"websiteUri":"https://www.dtdyxe.ca/?utm_source=GMBlisting&utm_medium=organic","regularOpeningHours":{"openNow":false,"periods":[{"open":{"day":1,"hour":7,"minute":30},"close":{"day":1,"hour":17,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":2,"hour":7,"minute":30},"close":{"day":2,"hour":17,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":3,"hour":7,"minute":30},"close":{"day":3,"hour":17,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":4,"hour":7,"minute":30},"close":{"day":4,"hour":17,"minute":0}},{"open":{"day":5,"hour":7,"minute":30},"close":{"day":5,"hour":17,"minute":0}}],"weekdayDescriptions":["Monday: 7:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Tuesday: 7:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Wednesday: 7:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Thursday: 7:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Friday: 7:30 AM – 5:00 PM","Saturday: Closed","Sunday: Closed"],"nextOpenTime":"2026-02-16T13:30:00Z"},"userRatingCount":204,"displayName":{"text":"Downtown Dental","languageCode":"en"},"primaryTypeDisplayName":{"text":"Dentist","languageCode":"en-US"},"reviews":[{"name":"places/ChIJdxXRGNH2BFMRm6-OFl60Thk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oeVpVZENOeTFPV0hCWlpFbFdkVmRKYkVORWFFRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"a month ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"I needed to have an emergency dental check up that did result in a molar extraction as the best course of action, although Dr. Tomchuk gave me all the options. This dentist is kind, patient, informative and skilled. Never felt the freezing, and gave me mini breaks for my comfort that made me feel more relaxed. I was referred here and will be back! The dental assistant was so helpful and the front desk reception warm and welcoming.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"I needed to have an emergency dental check up that did result in a molar extraction as the best course of action, although Dr. Tomchuk gave me all the options. This dentist is kind, patient, informative and skilled. Never felt the freezing, and gave me mini breaks for my comfort that made me feel more relaxed. I was referred here and will be back! The dental assistant was so helpful and the front desk reception warm and welcoming.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Judy Dawson","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105803925563938259861/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKFaOJXo_oc9v1Iq_2laHmk663iXEsw2f0dEmVeQIBPYedR6A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2026-01-07T00:55:30.523807945Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oeVpVZENOeTFPV0hCWlpFbFdkVmRKYkVORWFFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oeVpVZENOeTFPV0hCWlpFbFdkVmRKYkVORWFFRRAB!2m1!1s0x5304f6d118d11577:0x194eb45e168eaf9b"},{"name":"places/ChIJdxXRGNH2BFMRm6-OFl60Thk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4M2VsSlVXVEoxY2tKTFQwSTBRVEJYVW1GQ2FsRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"2 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"I have been a patient at Downtown Dental for decades. The clinic, the front desk staff, the dental assistants and the dentists are all wonderful. They are professional and friendly and provide excellent dental care! I saw Dr. Tomchak today for an extraction. He went the extra mile to be sure I was comfortable and had all the information. The extraction was quick and painless. Thank you Downtown Dental!","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"I have been a patient at Downtown Dental for decades. The clinic, the front desk staff, the dental assistants and the dentists are all wonderful. They are professional and friendly and provide excellent dental care! I saw Dr. Tomchak today for an extraction. He went the extra mile to be sure I was comfortable and had all the information. The extraction was quick and painless. Thank you Downtown Dental!","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Carol Lewis","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112670303671026940573/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIx2IqRKiunJ1doXtxpSJf3bbBHZrnv_Tb98wBCMUfxlbvkpA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2025-12-03T18:15:49.434354750Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4M2VsSlVXVEoxY2tKTFQwSTBRVEJYVW1GQ2FsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t4M2VsSlVXVEoxY2tKTFQwSTBRVEJYVW1GQ2FsRRAB!2m1!1s0x5304f6d118d11577:0x194eb45e168eaf9b"},{"name":"places/ChIJdxXRGNH2BFMRm6-OFl60Thk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxSmFsVkZVMHBRVm1rMU9FRklkR0pHVm01elkxRRAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"5 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"Awesome experience with Dr Trong. I have never seen such a caring dentist ever in my life. My whole family loved him and get all of our treatments from him!! He is 10/10. I was very anxious on the day of my treatment and he makes me feel very comfortable and did the entire treatment. He designed a great plan for me according to my needs. We are so happy we found him. And staff overall was very helpful. The dental assistant was very nice and the front receptionist was great. Overall I had great experience.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Awesome experience with Dr Trong. I have never seen such a caring dentist ever in my life. My whole family loved him and get all of our treatments from him!! He is 10/10. I was very anxious on the day of my treatment and he makes me feel very comfortable and did the entire treatment. He designed a great plan for me according to my needs. We are so happy we found him. And staff overall was very helpful. The dental assistant was very nice and the front receptionist was great. Overall I had great experience.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Fari Fari","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105624578843561237508/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_nMJ2i7Q_64efPpzZyg_hunCypsCuZ96C6X6BpRqXGewx4w=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"},"publishTime":"2025-09-16T17:10:01.292764410Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxSmFsVkZVMHBRVm1rMU9FRklkR0pHVm01elkxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2kxSmFsVkZVMHBRVm1rMU9FRklkR0pHVm01elkxRRAB!2m1!1s0x5304f6d118d11577:0x194eb45e168eaf9b"},{"name":"places/ChIJdxXRGNH2BFMRm6-OFl60Thk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ZelR6SkVNVkZyUjNOV1VtNHlWREJIU0c5T2MyYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"a month ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"Great with Kids!! All our kids have had great experiences here. Especially Dr. Sam Kirkpatrick… she is phenomenal and the front desk, hygienist team, everyone is so kind!  Highly recommend!","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"Great with Kids!! All our kids have had great experiences here. Especially Dr. Sam Kirkpatrick… she is phenomenal and the front desk, hygienist team, everyone is so kind!  Highly recommend!","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Lukas Bonnett","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103315667002671658909/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLtNWu_aQFqK1J2-g2S0VPo2T5h81cVGilI_VXa0ZLRojUOvQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2026-01-10T06:02:49.336241598Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ZelR6SkVNVkZyUjNOV1VtNHlWREJIU0c5T2MyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1","googleMapsUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25ZelR6SkVNVkZyUjNOV1VtNHlWREJIU0c5T2MyYxAB!2m1!1s0x5304f6d118d11577:0x194eb45e168eaf9b"},{"name":"places/ChIJdxXRGNH2BFMRm6-OFl60Thk/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21FemNuRnNNR3R6YWtaTE0ySjZWR0pEWnpaMmFIYxAB","relativePublishTimeDescription":"3 months ago","rating":5,"text":{"text":"My family has gone to Downtown Dental for most of our lives, but this past week showed me just how fortunate we have been to receive such excellent dental care.\n\nMy mom went in for a tooth ache amid unrelated, ongoing health issues.  They got her in quickly with Dr. Truong who showed such extreme care and compassion, ensuring a thorough and complete solution to her discomfort.  Both Dr. Truong and Dr. Tomchuk, who later performed needed procedures, followed-up with phone calls and referrals to ensure everything was taken care of before starting a treatment path for her other health issues.  I can’t express my gratitude enough for the incredible team at Downtown Dental.","languageCode":"en"},"originalText":{"text":"My family has gone to Downtown Dental for most of our lives, but this past week showed me just how fortunate we have been to receive such excellent dental care.\n\nMy mom went in for a tooth ache amid unrelated, ongoing health issues.  They got her in quickly with Dr. Truong who showed such extreme care and compassion, ensuring a thorough and complete solution to her discomfort.  Both Dr. Truong and Dr. Tomchuk, who later performed needed procedures, followed-up with phone calls and referrals to ensure everything was taken care of before starting a treatment path for her other health issues.  I can’t express my gratitude enough for the incredible team at Downtown Dental.","languageCode":"en"},"authorAttribution":{"displayName":"Craig Dubray","uri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108965546942892271458/reviews","photoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9oY1QT3goQ2UByd0qo3Vmp7J-cR86febmINWnBO8aHPMKliQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},"publishTime":"2025-10-26T04:06:09.323061356Z","flagContentUri":"https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?pos